{"title":"倾听夏日（组诗）","authors":["张大勇"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":8,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听夏日（组诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"○张大勇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛙歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵一朵的，开在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秧苗和绿之间，开在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池荷和画之间……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮起村庄和田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漾动月光和鼾声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛙歌！泥土和水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这两唇间唱出的民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上及天籁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下触根须"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远时，在辛稼轩的词中押韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近时，领动我的心跳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声长一寸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秧们就蹿高一寸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛙歌，你最高的音域"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标出了十月丰收的刻度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛙歌，平平仄仄的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自农历深处响起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听啦，听啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥漫整个乡村的稻花香哟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酽浓得在叫在唱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝉鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿枝丫间斑驳的光线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，款款地走下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到长长的丝瓜藤上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开满淡黄淡黄的音符"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听听听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童年的我，青嫩嫩的我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一转眼，被你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯成高高的个头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，不断地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摩我的耳廓，我的心灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一句农谚抚得又熟又香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不冷不热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五谷不结"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声，扩大清凉的雷声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划出滋润领地的雷声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电熄了之后，你没有逝去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你留下来，在乡村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在圆如鼓面的荷叶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在西瓜光滑的青皮上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在唐诗一样清澈的河面上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是欸乃欸乃……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，我的乡亲们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将手伸出窗外，伸进农谚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揪一把雨丝，放在耳边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们咧嘴笑了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们听到——你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领着高粱，领着稻菽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领着生长和果香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足音铿锵地向前跑着，跑着……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}